      <lg xml:id="TolE0437">
<l>oṉṟumuta loṉpā ṉiṟuti muṉṉar</l>
<l>niṉṟa patta ṉoṟṟukkeṭa vāytam</l>
<l>vantiṭa nilaiyu miyaṟkait teṉpa</l>
<l>kūṟiya viyaṟkai kuṟṟiya lukara</l>
<l>māṟa ṉiṟuti yalvaḻi yāṉa</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>And when [words denoting] weight and measure occur, the empty</l>
<l>morph <foreign xml:lang="ta">iṉ</foreign> will indeed not disappear.<note
              place="foot">E.g. <foreign xml:lang="ta">patiṉkaḻañcu</foreign> or <foreign xml:lang="ta">patiṉkalam.</foreign></note></l>
      </lg>
    </div>
